Price was given time to negotiate a deal with tax officials in October.At the time, lawyers for HMRC told judge Jonathan Middleton they had been informed of a proposal by Ms Price for an Individual Voluntary Agreement.The IVA lets people with debt repay their creditors at an affordable rate, to avoid bankruptcy.
            

